    public abstract class SchedulableConnector
extends DeviceConnector
implements ISchedulable
    The class SchedulableConnector implements a connector between the IController and the ISchedulable interfaces.

    Description

    It implements the required interface IController and in the methods it calls the corresponding offered method ISchedulable.

    Created on : 2020-01-27
